data.description: Introducing a highly-maintained single-level residence where comfort meets modern design! This beauty offers an easy-care landscape, palm trees, a 2-car garage, and an RV gate. Be greeted by a spacious living room featuring a corner gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings, wood-look vinyl flooring, and sliding glass doors, making entertaining a bliss. Make your way to the gourmet eat-in kitchen, providing stainless steel appliances, white shaker cabinetry, quartz counters, and track lighting. The main bedroom is a true retreat, boasting plush carpeting underfoot, outdoor access, and a private bathroom with dual sinks and a step-in shower. New dual pane windows throughout for energy efficiency! The tranquil backyard, with a covered patio and artificial turf, is the perfect oasis for outdoor entertainment or peaceful solitude. Whether it’s enjoying a morning coffee, hosting a weekend BBQ, or simply soaking up the sun, this private space adds significant value to the home.
